channel.title: Rune-Force 639 [Release]
channel.description:
[center][size=18pt][b]Rune-Force 639[/b][/size][/center]
Feature: - All Bosses Work - All Skills Work - Unique Dungeoneering System - Barrows - 100% God Wars - Corporeal Beast - Crystal Key Chest - Ancient Effigy drops - Level Up Your Farming For A Wicked Cape - Get Access To Frost Dragons, If You Have 85 Dungeoneering - Full Agility - Full Hunter System - Ice Strykewyrms - Jad - Nex - Torms - Summoning - Teleporting Crystals - Bork - Chaos Elemental - Forinthry Dungeon - Wildy Wyrm - Christmas Event
[b][size=18pt]Pictures:[/size][b]
Kill all the god wars bosses for elite drops! [img]http://img708.imageshack.us/img708/1523/bandosnpc.png[/img]
Barrow brothers ready for the slayin' [img]http://img853.imageshack.us/img853/2748/barrowsj.png[/img]
Crystal Key Chest; Exchange your crystal key for random items [img]http://img856.imageshack.us/img856/4923/chestb.png[/img]
Corporeal Beast; Now with all attack styles [img]http://img502.imageshack.us/img502/4150/corpw.png[/img]
Level up your Dungeoneering, and gain access to cool weapons [img]http://img593.imageshack.us/img593/7015/dungu.png[/img]
Get Ancient Effigy drops [img]http://img141.imageshack.us/img141/2048/effy.png[/img]
Level up your farming for a wicked cape [img]http://img190.imageshack.us/img190/8717/farmingz.png[/img]
If you have 85 Dungeoneering, get access to Frost Dragons [img]http://img525.imageshack.us/img525/674/frostie.png[/img]
Full Agility [img]http://img228.imageshack.us/img228/4373/gnomecourse.png[/img]
Excellent Hunter System [img]http://img32.imageshack.us/img32/5630/hunteri.png[/img]
Ice Strykewyrms; get your Staff of Light [img]http://img842.imageshack.us/img842/8706/icestryk.png[/img]
TzTok-Jad [img]http://img72.imageshack.us/img72/2963/jad.png[/img]
Nex is waiting for your soul [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/jhNZ3K.png[/img]
Full tormented demons [img]http://img214.imageshack.us/img214/2962/tdsi.png[/img]
Summoning [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/cTZDgV.png[/img]
Teleport Crystal for saving an area you want to teleport too! [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/ZmBHWP.png[/img]
Bork [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/J1cPxt.png[/img]
Chaos Elemental, in the deep wilderness! [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/HDsc0L.png[/img]
Forinthry Dungeon [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/2y1NOu.png[/img]
Dungeoneering [img]http://i.imgur.com/Zxsie.png[/img]
Christmas Event [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/0rSWGE.png[/img]
Wildy Wyrm [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/eUyUgV.png[/img]
[b][size=18pt]I will be starting on V2 if you have any suggestions, please feel free to comment them.[/size][/b]
[b][size=18pt]Download:[/size][/b]
[url=http://up.ht/PmmkOT]http://up.ht/PmmkOT[/url]
[b][size=12pt]I hope you enjoy this release! Remember to Rep++.[/size][/b]
[size=14pt][b]Credits:[/b][/size] - Dementhium team - Me
